<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''哮吼'''（Croup），又稱'''咽喉氣管支氣管炎'''（laryngotracheobronchitis）為一種[[呼吸道感染|呼吸道感染症]]，通常是由[[病毒|病毒]]感染所誘發。感染會引致[[氣管|氣管]]內腫脹，影響正常呼吸，並產生如狗吠般的或破鑼般刺耳的[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]聲、吸氣{{tsl|en|stridor|喘鳴}}、[[沙啞|聲音沙啞]]等典型症狀。有時也會合併[[发热|发热]]或流鼻水的症狀<ref name="Au10">{{Cite journal|title=Croup - assessment and management|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20485713|last=Rajapaksa|first=Shabna|last2=Starr|first2=Mike|date=2010-05|journal=Australian Family Physician|issue=5|volume=39|pages=280–282|issn=0300-8495|pmid=20485713|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116124338/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20485713/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。症狀可能或輕或重，最常於夜間開始發作或惡化<ref name="Au10" /><ref name="Croup09">{{Cite journal|title=Croup|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2907784/|last=Johnson|first=David Wyatt|date=2009-03-10|journal=BMJ Clinical Evidence|volume=2009|issn=1752-8526|pmc=2907784|pmid=19445760|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2022-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220402163620/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2907784/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一般而言，哮吼會持續一至二天<ref name="Thom2013">{{Cite journal|title=Duration of symptoms of respiratory tract infections in children: systematic review|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3898587/|last=Thompson|first=Matthew|last2=Vodicka|first2=Talley A|date=2013-12-11|journal=The BMJ|doi=10.1136/bmj.f7027|volume=347|issn=0959-8138|pmc=3898587|pmid=24335668|last3=Blair|first3=Peter S|last4=Buckley|first4=David I|last5=Heneghan|first5=Carl|last6=Hay|first6=Alastair D|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211145414/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3898587/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
可能引起哮吼的病毒包括{{tsl|en|parainfluenza|副流感病毒}}及[[正黏液病毒科|流感病毒]]<ref name="Au10" />。偶見肇因於[[病原细菌|細菌感染]]<ref name="Cherry08">{{Cite journal|title=Clinical practice. Croup|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18216359|last=Cherry|first=James D.|date=2008-01-24|journal=The New England Journal of Medicine|issue=4|doi=10.1056/NEJMcp072022|volume=358|pages=384–391|issn=1533-4406|pmid=18216359|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905201000/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18216359/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。診斷時必須排除其他可能更危險的疾病，如[[会厌炎|会厌炎]]或{{tsl|en|airway foreign body|呼吸道異物|呼吸道異物阻塞}}等等。更進一步的檢查包含血液檢查、[[X射线|X射线]]，以及病原體培養等等，但一般不須進行<ref name="PedN09">{{Cite journal|title=Acute bronchiolitis and croup|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19135584|last=Everard|first=Mark L.|date=2009-02|journal=Pediatric Clinics of North America|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.pcl.2008.10.007|volume=56|pages=119–133, x–xi|issn=0031-3955|pmid=19135584|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115194336/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19135584/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Prevention and treatment -->
接種[[流行性感冒|流行性感冒]]和[[白喉|白喉]]疫苗可以預防許多哮吼的發生<ref name=Cherry08/>。治療方式則一般給予單劑口服[[甾體|類固醇]]。更嚴重的病例可能需給予吸入性[[肾上腺素|肾上腺素]]<ref name="Au10" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Nebulized epinephrine for croup in children|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24114291|last=Bjornson|first=Candice|last2=Russell|first2=Kelly|date=2013-10-10|journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=10|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD006619.pub3|pages=CD006619|issn=1469-493X|pmid=24114291|last3=Vandermeer|first3=Ben|last4=Klassen|first4=Terry P.|last5=Johnson|first5=David W.|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902192749/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24114291/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有1-5%的病例可能需要住院<ref name="CMAJ2013">{{Cite journal|title=Croup in children|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3796596/|last=Bjornson|first=Candice L.|last2=Johnson|first2=David W.|date=2013-10-15|journal=CMAJ : Canadian Medical Association Journal|issue=15|doi=10.1503/cmaj.121645|volume=185|pages=1317–1323|issn=0820-3946|pmc=3796596|pmid=23939212|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111224036/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3796596/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

<!-- Epidemiology and history -->
哮吼為相對常見的疾病症狀，约15％的儿童曾經或正在罹患此病。患者通常集中於6个月到5岁之間，少見15歲以上的患者<ref name="Croup09" /><ref name="PedN09" />。男性患者較女性稍多，一般集中於秋季發生<ref name="CMAJ2013" />。在[[白喉疫苗|白喉疫苗]]發明之前，許多哮吼是因[[白喉|白喉]]誘發，且可能有致死危險<ref name=Cherry08/><ref>{{cite book|last1=Steele|first1=Volney|title=Bleed, blister, and purge : a history of medicine on the American frontier|date=2005|publisher=Mountain Press|location=Missoula, Mont.|isbn=978-0-87842-505-1|page=324}}</ref>。西方國家因[[百白破疫苗|白喉疫苗]]成功，因此此類哮吼症非常少見<ref name="history">{{cite book|author=Feigin, Ralph D.|title=Textbook of pediatric infectious diseases|publisher=Saunders|location=Philadelphia|year=2004|page=252|isbn=0-7216-9329-6}}</ref>。

